definitions.definition: An area on both sides of the river Rhine , in the west of Germany . Roughly equivalent to the former Prussian Rhine Province , now the greater part of Rhineland-Palatinate plus the south-western half of North Rhine-Westphalia .
All of Germany's territories on the Rhine.
A village in Montgomery County , Missouri , United States .
An unincorporated community in Knox County , Texas , United States .
A rural municipality in southern Manitoba , Canada .
A hamlet in Norfolk County , Ontario , Canada .
